{
  "texts": [
    "Refer to Appendix B for further details about these models.",
    "The decoder-only implementation of the multiple-choice reading comprehension system is based upon the pretrained instruction finetuned Llama2-7B model foot_2.",
    "ELECTRA-base (Clark et al., 2020) is selected for the data complexity evaluator models.",
    "The pretrained model is finetuned on the RACE++ train split with the complexity class (easy, medium or hard) as the label.",
    "Hyperparameter tuning details are given in Appendix B for both the reading comprehension and data complexity classifier systems."
  ]
}